{"tid":2337829,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"111影視名人聯署 抵制《延禧》製作人","createTime":"2020-12-23T14:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T15:45:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f70c858f2e1ad3df1c1c7450e5b756d20500c5e5","tid":2337829,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201223/UA7SEDMJDFDC7DOWIWU4L66RRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201223%2FUA7SEDMJDFDC7DOWIWU4L66RRU%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp6wvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=b25ba7eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201223%2FUA7SEDMJDFDC7DOWIWU4L66RRU%2F&h=443fbb37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201223/UA7SEDMJDFDC7DOWIWU4L66RRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n111影視名人聯署 抵制《延禧》製作人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JQQ7jY4dOOT_bY8ZTMJnE_xZZAo=/1559x1054/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3X7ERL3PYBHN7BOSCSOKVT4CPU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJQQ7jY4dOOT_bY8ZTMJnE_xZZAo%3D%2F1559x1054%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3X7ERL3PYBHN7BOSCSOKVT4CPU.gif&h=6d543e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國著名作家及導演郭敬明、《延禧攻略》製作人于正近日分別擔任綜藝節目的導師，教授影視行業心得，其作狀激起包括著名台灣作家瓊瑤等兩岸111名著名影視界幕後人員不齒，前晚發聯名公開信怒轟為「文賊」，指摘兩人抄襲成風，漠視法院要求道歉命令，呼籲業界「拒絕劣迹且不加悔改的創作人，從公眾媒體驅逐出去」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「文賊」拒法院道歉令<br />\n<br />\n聯署信大罵于正及郭敬明在節目只是話題炒作，做法引起業界極大反感。信中引述郭、于兩人都曾被法院判決抄襲，但拒絕執行法院道歉命令：「這樣的『文賊』卻在販賣成功學，在社會上造成極其惡劣影響」。信中又反問：「吸毒嫖娼的藝人都受到懲罰，一些有道德問題的藝人都限制出境，為甚麼被法院判決的『文賊』卻被資本及平台追捧？」<br />\n<br />\n連署人的名單裏包括瓊瑤，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"483380cf98526af9a20f7dafd66915c24e07890b","tid":2337829,"uid":12312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95b1f41db158c753588ac82e79db4dbcd646333","tid":2337829,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:40:24.000Z","msg":"抄乜？"},{"pid":"5effb69d5d9cb650f317a6c2ffe30158a140c298","tid":2337829,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"郭敬明係咪之前做戲節目俾爾東聲屌果個"}]}